com.thinkaurelius.titan.diskstorage.locking.consistentkey

Class LockClaim

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thinkaurelius.titan.diskstorage.locking.consistentkey.LockClaim

  • public class LockClaim
extends Object
    An attempted lock.

    Contains the key, column, and expected-value at the key-column coordinate in some underlying store. A reference to the store is also indirectly maintained through a LockConfig instance passed to the constructor.

    Author:
    Dan LaRocque
    See Also:
    ConsistentKeyLockTransaction
